summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2800, for the improvement of the east side of east waterway from Spokane Street to Dakota Street, and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues all in the City of Seattle, by the construction of a bulkhead of brush and piles or other suitable material, under Ordinance No. 33497 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
